OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,FThe parents of a three-year-old boy
OL,7,Fwho died from sepsis after being
OL,8,Fmisdiagnosed say they struggle to deal
OL,9,Fwith the "madness" caused by his death.
OL,11,FOscar Neillings died at Chesterfield
OL,12,FRoyal Hospital in November 2023, about
OL,13,Fa week after contracting a
OL,14,Fstreptococcus A infection.
OL,16,FAn inquest at Chesterfield Coroner's
OL,17,FCourt has heard two GPs had mistakenly
OL,18,Fdiagnosed his cold symptoms as a viral
OL,19,Finfection before he was referred to
OL,20,Fhospital.
