OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,FHospital staff then failed to
OL,7,Fadminister antibiotics for more than
OL,8,Ftwo hours after he was admitted.
OL,10,FA jury found on Friday that neglect
OL,11,Fhad contributed to his death.
OL,13,FOscar's mother Stephanie said she and
OL,14,Fher husband, Mark, try to maintain
OL,15,Fnormality for their other two
OL,16,Fchildren, Poppy and Maxwell.
OL,18,FShe said: "It's so hard to cover
OL,19,Feverything up. I think we both have
OL,20,Fgot this amazing mask that we put on
OL,21,Fto cover everything with a smile.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
