OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,F"I can't believe this is our life.
OL,7,FIt's utter madness."
OL,9,FThe inquest heard Oscar, who was
OL,10,Fdescribed by his parents as "a ball of
OL,11,Fenergy" who was "fun loving",
OL,12,Fdeveloped a cold about a week before
OL,13,Fhis death from which he never
OL,14,Frecovered.
OL,16,FAs his symptoms worsened, they twice
OL,17,Fcalled the NHS 111 helpline, leading
OL,18,Fto separate out-of-hours GP
OL,19,Fappointments.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
