OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,FBoth doctors said Oscar had a viral
OL,7,Finfection and did not think he needed
OL,8,Fto be referred to hospital, the court
OL,9,Fwas told.
OL,11,FIt was only when he developed
OL,12,Fabdominal pain, vomiting, and
OL,13,Fbreathing difficulties that a third GP
OL,14,Freferred him to hospital on 8 November
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FMedical experts told the hearing
OL,18,FOscar's care was fragmented and lacked
OL,19,Furgency. He died from a cardiac arrest
OL,20,Fthe same day.
