OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,F"He was just so wonderful and it's so
OL,7,Fhard to believe that he's gone. I
OL,8,Fdon't think I actually do believe that.
OL,10,F"We were meant to be planning for his
OL,11,Fschool place in the December but
OL,12,Finstead we were planning his funeral."
OL,14,FThe couple are warning other parents
OL,15,Fto be aware of the signs of sepsis and
OL,16,Fare calling for the condition to be
OL,17,Fgiven greater recognition.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/8
