OL,3,C'We cover everything with a smile':
OL,4,CParents of three-year-old sepsis victim
OL,6,FMrs Neillings said: "It should be
OL,7,Ftreated as a medical emergency, the
OL,8,Fsame as a heart attack of stroke, and
OL,9,Fthat is what the UK Sepsis Trust are
OL,10,Fpushing for.
OL,12,F"If the general public are aware and
OL,13,Fthey can actually go into a medical
OL,14,Fenvironment and say 'could this be
OL,15,Fsepsis?' and actually use the word,
OL,16,Fbecause as soon as it's out there then
OL,17,Fit gets people thinking."
